comment: James (CLE) and Schroder (ATL) make incidental contact with one another during rebounding.

Horford (ATL) maintains legal guarding position as he defends James's (CLE) shot attempt.
Millsap (ATL) maintains legal guarding position as he defends James's (CLE) shot attempt.
Millsap (ATL) and James (CLE) briefly engage and separate during rebounding.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court was overturned and possession awarded to CLE.

Millsap (ATL) makes contact with the ball after it has touched the backboard.

Horford (ATL) sets the screen on Dellavedova (CLE) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
